<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>404 - Page non trouvée</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #000;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .navbar {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: #000;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #00adb5;
      color: white;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .navbar a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #00adb5;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .main-content {
      margin-top: 120px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #00adb5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    a {
      color: #00adb5;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

        /* Taille de l'image dans la navbar */
    .navbar img {
      height: 36px;
      width: 36px;
      margin-right: 0.7rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="{{ route('home') }}"><img src="@/images/icone.ico">DeckStorm</a>
  </div>

  <div class="main-content">
    <h1>404 - Page non trouvée</h1>
    <p>
      Cette page n'existe pas. Retournez à la 
      <a href="{{ route('home') }}">page d'accueil</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
